cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a new trajectory generation approach using a modified LSTM-based car following model. This involves improvements to the traditional LSTM model structure and training method to reduce error propagation in the temporal and spatial dimensions. The paper's focus on machine learning and optimization techniques suggests that it is most likely to belong to the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper's application in traffic engineering and micro-simulation also suggests that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
